1983;;Better Late Than Never;;American;;Bryan Forbes;;David Niven, Maggie Smith, Art Carney;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Better_Late_Than_Never_(film);;Nick (Niven) is the supposed grandfather of 10-year-old Bridget (Partridge), who stands to inherit a sizeable fortune. Charley (Carney) shows up and claims that he is the genuine grandpa. Both men once slept with Bridget's grandmother, and she was never certain which of the two produced her child. Neither Nick nor Charley are good prospects, so Bridget must choose from the lesser of two evils.